		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/11/anyone-want-to-buy-a-used-car/" rel="bookmark">Anyone want to buy a used car?</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>That ticking is getting louder, I tell ya.<br />
We&#8217;re officially out of the &#8220;long vacation&#8221; timeframe, and into the &#8220;standard&#8221; two week vacation timeframe. You know this one: enough time to fly to a distant land, see two or three different places, get really drunk in a bar and get robbed blind, realise you&#8217;ve actually got a funky disease you&#8217;re not sure if you got from the food or that person you swore looked like a woman the night before&#8230;<br />
What? Why are you looking at me like that? You make it sound like no-one else has vacations like that.<br />
